              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  The following are equivalent for a distributive lattice <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>:
  <html:ol><html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-75C1/" title="Local distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-75C1/" display-uri="idem-comm-75C1" type="local">local</fr:link>.</html:li>
