            <fr:uri>https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-S892/</fr:uri>
            <fr:display-uri>idem-comm-S892</fr:display-uri>
            <fr:route>/idem-comm-S892/</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Prime spectra of local and integral distributive lattices">Prime spectra of local and integral distributive lattices</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="/idem-comm-75C1/" title="Local distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-75C1/" display-uri="idem-comm-75C1" type="local">local</fr:link>. Then since <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> has a minimal filter <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\{1\}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> has a <html:em>root</html:em>, which we denote as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bot ]]></fr:tex>. Dually, if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-487K/" title="Integral distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-487K/" display-uri="idem-comm-487K" type="local">integral</fr:link>, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> has a focal point, which we usually denote as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\top ]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors />
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
              <fr:month>6</fr:month>
              <fr:day>11</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:uri>https://charloced.github.io/schm-Q0A2/</fr:uri>
            <fr:display-uri>schm-Q0A2</fr:display-uri>
            <fr:route>/schm-Q0A2/</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Morphisms of local spectra into a scheme">Morphisms of local spectra into a scheme</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Proposition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>
  Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="/idem-comm-75C1/" title="Local distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-75C1/" display-uri="idem-comm-75C1" type="local">local</fr:link>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> a <fr:link href="/schm-86OJ/" title="Scheme" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-86OJ/" display-uri="schm-86OJ" type="local">scheme</fr:link>. A map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : \operatorname {Spec} A \to  X]]></fr:tex> always factors through the inclusion <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec}{\mathcal {O}_{X,x}} \to  X]]></fr:tex> specified in <fr:link href="/schm-MWRT/" title="Affine scheme at a stalk" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" /></fr:link>, where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x = f(\bot )]]></fr:tex> for the <fr:link href="/idem-comm-S892/" title="Prime spectra of local and integral distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-S892/" display-uri="idem-comm-S892" type="local">root</fr:link> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex>,
  
  <html:figure><fr:resource hash="51b4ab336e52fc582b78fc7e64af7fa6"><fr:resource-content><html:img src="/51b4ab336e52fc582b78fc7e64af7fa6.svg" /></fr:resource-content><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="preamble"><![CDATA[\usepackage {tikz-cd}\usepackage {quiver}]]></fr:resource-source><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="body"><![CDATA[
    \begin {tikzcd}
      {\mathrm {Spec}\,A} & {\mathrm {Spec}\,\mathcal  O_{X,x}} \\
      & X
      \arrow [dashed, from=1-1, to=1-2]
      \arrow ["f"', from=1-1, to=2-2]
      \arrow [from=1-2, to=2-2]
    \end {tikzcd}
  ]]></fr:resource-source></fr:resource></html:figure>

  In particular, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A \to  \operatorname {Spec}\mathcal {O}_{X,x}]]></fr:tex> preserves the root, or in other words <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {O}_{X,x} \to  A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-QQEF/" title="T-conservative and f-conservative maps" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-QQEF/" display-uri="idem-comm-QQEF" type="local">t-conservative</fr:link>.
</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors /><fr:date><fr:year>2025</fr:year><fr:month>6</fr:month><fr:day>11</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  On the level of set, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> evidently factors through <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec}{\mathcal {O}_{X,x}}]]></fr:tex> since as shown in <fr:link href="/schm-MWRT/" title="Affine scheme at a stalk" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" /></fr:link> the latter is <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\uparrow {x} = \uparrow {f(\bot )}]]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> as a continuous map is in particular monotone. Then since at the level of stalks we have a t-conservative map
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ f^{\sharp }_\bot  : \mathcal {O}_{X,x} \to  \mathcal {O}_{A,\bot } \cong  A, ]]></fr:tex>
  this induces a map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A \to  \operatorname {Spec}\mathcal {O}_{X,x}]]></fr:tex> which indeed when post-composed with the inclusion <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec}\mathcal {O}_{X,x} \to  X]]></fr:tex> gives us <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>. This can be seen easily when <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is affine, and the general case is trivial from the proof of <fr:link href="/schm-MWRT/" title="Affine scheme at a stalk" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-MWRT/" display-uri="schm-MWRT" /></fr:link>.
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors />
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
              <fr:month>6</fr:month>
